data.text:
This article is about the American morning block on Nickelodeon. For the 24/7 channel, see Nick Jr. Channel. For other uses, see Nick Jr. (disambiguation).

Nick Jr. (sometimes disambiguated as Nick Jr. on Nickelodeon or Nick Jr. on Nick, and sometimes referred to as Nick, Jr.) is an American morning programming block that airs on Nickelodeon every weekday. It was launched on January 4, 1988. Nick Jr. features a lineup of shows aimed at children aged 2 through 6.
